Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I'm on Page 02 of Thoracic CT
Then 'Anamnesis' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Nicotine abuse' from 'Anamnesis' dropdown menu
Then 'Add anamnesis' button is enabled
And 'Pack years' input field is enabled

When I click 'Add anamnesis' button
Then a second dropdown menu is enabled and automatically selected
And 'Add anamnesis' button is disabled
